quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  63,9,"O you who believe, do not let your wealth and your children distract you from Allah’s remembrance. For whoever does that, it is they who are the losers"
  63,10,"And spend from what We have provided for you before death comes to one of you, then he would say, “My Lord, If only You had delayed me for a short while, so that I would give in charity and be one of the righteous.”"
  63,11,"But Allah will never delay a soul when its appointed time comes, and Allah is All-Aware of what you do"